{"tid":1908872,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"賣P95 8577 270蚊一盒十個","createTime":"2020-03-03T14:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T18:52:24.000Z","uid":316805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"06760ed2d2a16bbff00c01d1cfa9be04c587ca24","tid":1908872,"uid":316805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:41:52.000Z","msg":"3M&trade; 8577 P95 防微量有機氣體即棄口罩&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nP95 即棄式口罩<br />\n<br />\n阻隔油性和非油性顆粒<br />\n<br />\n口罩配有活性碳層可過濾微量有機氣體 活性碳吸附層可吸附厭惡的有機蒸氣<br />\n<br />\nN代表非抗油 not resistant to oil 代表濾材不能使用於含有油氣的環境<br />\n<br />\nP代表耐油 oil proof 代表可完全隔離油氣<br />\n<br />\n95代表對直徑&nbsp;0.3&mu;m&nbsp;以上粒子的阻隔能力達95%<br />\n<br />\n雖然流感病毒或是武漢肺炎的新型冠狀病毒等病毒尺寸本身約在0.1 &mu;ｍ左右，但因為這些病毒通常是依附於「飛沫」中，並透過飛沫進行傳染。因此，只要能夠隔絕大小約在3.0～5.0&mu;m的飛沫，就可以達到防止病毒直接由飛沫傳遞造成感染的效果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟拗咗好耐先至搵到貨源<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n揾舖頭代購要比錢同埋運費嗰啲支出<br />\n<br />\n其實冇賺 良心價發售<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想買就私訊 tg@cookedsalmon <br />\n<br />\n比錢先 如果貨源突然出現問題將會提供退款<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以銀行過數，轉帳同轉數快比錢<br />\n<br />\n黨鐵 東鐵綫 觀塘綫 屯馬綫 荃灣綫交收(唔入閘)<br />\n<br />\n利申: 第一次係連登賣嘢 如果做得唔啱請屌醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f0975d9532d264e229c08a4f3c3b06b0b5c253","tid":1908872,"uid":55200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:42:55.000Z","msg":"入數黨"},{"pid":"83c3f81844ad4a178f4cf3eee43788da754f0c2e","tid":1908872,"uid":316805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKnwPQJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKnwPQJ.jpg&h=f7c2cd9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L45Kqo4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL45Kqo4.jpg&h=1b077756&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c8cb460c9748